<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="smile-n">smile <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /smaɪl/    美 /smaɪl/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>微笑；笑容：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have / wear a smile
面带微笑</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In a word, let’s greet every day <strong>with a smile</strong>.
总之，让我们微笑着迎接每一天吧。</p><footer>2009 福建书面表达</footer></div></div>